        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="chu">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_00068/">азъ</w> <persName ref="names.xml#n007">герг</persName> <w lemma="поглѧдат">поглѧда<supplied reason = "lost">хь</supplied></w>  
                    <lb n="2"/> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_02178/">долѹ</w> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_02992/"></w> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_01887/">горѣ</w> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_02992/"></w> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_08268/">рекохъ</w>   
                    <lb n="3"/> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_00647/"><expan><abbr>б</abbr><ex>ож</ex><abbr>е</abbr></expan></w> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_04753/">на</w> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_03254/">мѧ</w> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_09646/">твое</w> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_03060/">зба
                    <lb n="4" break="no"/>в</w> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_05470/">нъ</w> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_06051/">ѿ</w> <w lemma="татарнъ">татаръ</w> 
                </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <head xml:lang="bg">Букви в лигатура:</head> 
                    <head xml:lang="en">Letters in ligatures:</head>
                         <app loc="1"> <note>п (герг поглѧда[хь])</note></app>
                         <app loc="3"> <note>м (мѧ)</note></app>
                         <app loc="4"> <note>н (в нъ)</note> <note>ѿ (отъ)</note></app>
                </listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <seg xml:lang="bg"> 
                    Аз, Герги, погледнах
                    долу и горе и рекох:
                    "Боже, в името твое изба-
                    ви ни от татарите!"
                </seg>
                <seg xml:lang="en"> 
                    I, Gergi, looked 
                    down and looked up and said:
                    "God, in your name save
                    us from the tatars"
                </seg>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>
                    <seg xml:lang="bg"><note>Надписът е изписан върху камък на една от стените на Шуменската крепост.</note></seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en"><note>The inscription is carved on a stone, set in one of the walls of the Shumen Fortress.</note></seg>
                </p> 
            </div>
